remarks.format:
  
  
## Examples

Nell'esempio seguente viene ottenuta la proprietà Scheme corrente.

```csharp
BasicHttpBinding binding = new BasicHttpBinding();
string thisScheme = binding.Scheme;
```

  
  
## Examples

In questo esempio viene ottenuto il valore ReceiveSynchronously.

```csharp
BasicHttpBinding binding = new BasicHttpBinding();
IBindingRuntimePreferences s = (binding as IBindingRuntimePreferences);
bool receiveSynchronously = s.ReceiveSynchronously;
```
